'''殺戮樂團'''（{{lang-en|Slaughter}}）是來自美國[[內華達州|內華達州]][[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]的搖滾樂團，由主唱兼節奏吉他手[[馬克·斯勞特|馬克·斯勞特]]（Mark Slaughter）和貝斯手[[達納·斯特魯姆|達納·斯特魯姆]]（Dana Strum）於1988年成立<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ultimateclassicrock.com/vinnie-vincent-invasion-end/|title=Mark Slaughter Looks Back on the Band Mutiny That Ended the Vinnie Vincent Invasion|author=|website=Ultimateclassicrock.com|date=2016|accessdate=2016-08-29|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827165652/http://ultimateclassicrock.com/vinnie-vincent-invasion-end/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1990年以首張專輯《[[堅持下去|堅持下去]]》（''Stick It to Ya''）而聞名<ref name="LarkinHM">{{cite book|title=[[Encyclopedia_of_Popular_Music|The Guinness Who’s Who of Heavy Metal]]|editor=[[Colin_Larkin_(writer)|Colin Larkin]]|publisher=[[Guinness_Publishing|Guinness Publishing]]|date=1995|edition=Second|isbn=0-85112-656-1|page=[https://archive.org/details/guinnesswhoswhoo0000unse_z3v7_2/page/328 328]}}</ref>；該專輯包含幾首熱門歌曲，如〈[[徹夜未眠_(殺戮樂團歌曲)|徹夜未眠]]〉、〈Spend My Life〉、〈Mad About You〉和〈Fly to the Angels〉。專輯在美國達到了雙白金唱片認證<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.slaughterweb.com/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070217074848/http://www.slaughterweb.com/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2007-02-17|title=Slaughter|date=2007-02-17|website=Web.archive.org|accessdate=2019-11-23}}</ref>。樂團在全美穩定巡演至今。

